These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: coffee, fanta
Movie-Genre: crime, spy
Birthday: october, august
Flower: begonia, iris
1. Flower:iris is on the left or right of Birthday:august##3
2. Beverage:fanta is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:spy == Beverage:coffee##1
4. Flower:iris is on the right of Flower:begonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Birthday         | august | october |
| Flower     | begonia | iris    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: avocado, cabbage
Hobby: sudoku, rock-climbing
Color: emerald, turquise
Transport: motorbike, tram
1. Color:turquise is in an odd position##4
2. Hobby:sudoku == Transport:tram##1
3. Food:cabbage is on the right of Hobby:rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | sudoku  |
| Color           | turquise         | emerald     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################
 
