House: townhouse, craftsman
Pet: cat, horse
Sport: climbing, soccer
1. Sport:soccer is in an even position##4
2. House:craftsman is on the far left or far right##3
3. Birthday:october == House:townhouse##1
4. Pet:cat is on the left of House:craftsman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
